data.description: Discover this inviting single-level haven with an open floor plan in El Mirage! Once inside, you'll immediately notice the expansive great room featuring tile & carpet flooring, high vaulted ceilings, and tons of natural light. The kitchen offers track lighting, built-in appliances, cabinets with crown moulding, and a center island with a breakfast bar ideal for a quick midnight snack. You'll certainly love the impeccable primary bedroom equipped with a well-sized walk-in closet and a private bathroom with shower & tub combination. Check out the large backyard, which includes a covered patio for relaxation and mature trees that provide refreshing shade. What are you waiting for? This home is the one you're looking for!
